Package com.intellij.util.ui.update

Class Update

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.util.ui.update.ComparableObject.Impl
      • com.intellij.util.ui.update.Update
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComparableObject, java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DisposableUpdate

    public abstract class Update
extends ComparableObject.Impl
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Describes a task for MergingUpdateQueue. Equal tasks (instances with the equal identity objects) are merged, i.e. only the first of them is executed. If some tasks are more generic than others override canEat(Update) method.
    See Also:
    MergingUpdateQueue

      • canEat

        public boolean canEat(Update update)
        Override this method and return true if this task is more generic than the passed update, e.g. this tasks repaint the whole frame and the passed task repaint some component on the frame. In that case the less generic tasks will be removed from the queue before execution.
